sequenceDiagram
autonumber

participant Dev as push main
participant Actions as GitHub Actions
participant Pack as packaging-test
participant Smoke as smoke-test
participant Deploy as deploy-main.sh
participant Server as 目标服务器
participant Runtime as 平台运行环境

Dev->>Actions: 触发 deploy-main.yml
Actions->>Pack: 检查 SkyWalking / Prometheus / 部署配置
Pack-->>Actions: 通过

Actions->>Smoke: 启动完整环境并执行冒烟
Smoke->>Runtime: 验证节点注册、服务发现、targets、Trace
Smoke-->>Actions: 通过

Actions->>Deploy: SSH 执行部署脚本
Deploy->>Server: git fetch + checkout main
Deploy->>Runtime: docker compose up -d --build
Deploy->>Runtime: 等待前后端、Prometheus、Grafana、SkyWalking 健康
Deploy->>Runtime: warmup /api/demo-chain
Deploy->>Runtime: 等待业务 Trace 出现
Runtime-->>Deploy: 观测闭环成立
Deploy-->>Actions: 部署成功
